{"_id":"59HKbdpBIXfiJt91","name":"Occult Herbmaster","permission":{"default":0,"xVCY8TaEyq1Er5RJ":3},"type":"class","data":{"abilities":"<p>Tough as wood, roll 3d6+2 Toughness. Low in protein, roll 3d6-2 Strength. Roll d6 on the weapons table and d2 on the armor table. You carry a portable laboratory and continually search for frequently expended ingredients. Daily you have the materials to create two randomly determined decoctions and can brew a total of d4 doses. If unused they lose vitality after 24 hours.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Red Poison</li>\n<li>Ezumiels Vapor</li>\n<li>Southern Frog Stew</li>\n<li>Elixir Vitalis</li>\n<li>Spider-Owl Soup</li>\n<li>Fernor's Philtre</li>\n<li>Hyphos Enervating Snuff</li>\n<li>Black Poison</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;(d8) Probably raised in&hellip; but may also come from</p>\n<ol>\n<li>calm isolation in the Sarkash dark.</li>\n<li>calm isolation in the Sarkash dark.</li>\n<li>calm isolation in the Sarkash dark.</li>\n<li>the illegal midnight markets of Schleswig.</li>\n<li>the heretic isle of Cr&euml;lut, two nautical miles east of Grift.</li>\n<li>the old frozen ruins not far from Alli&aacute;ns.</li>\n<li>a little witches cottage in Galgenbeck.</li>\n<li>the runs of the Shadow King's manse, thick with memories of mushrooms and smoke.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","armorTableDie":"1d2","description":"Born of the mushroom, raised in the glade, watched by the eye of the moon in a silverblack pool.","omenDie":"1d2","startingAgility":"3d6","startingHitPoints":"1d6","startingItems":"morkborg.class-occult-herbmaster,Create Decoctions\nmorkborg.class-occult-herbmaster,Portable Laboratory","startingPresence":"3d6","startingRolls":"morkborg.rolls-occult-herbmaster,Occult Herbmaster Decoctions,2\nmorkborg.rolls-occult-herbmaster,Probably raised in,1","startingSilver":"2d6*10","startingStrength":"3d6-2","startingToughness":"3d6+2","weaponTableDie":"1d6"},"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/tokens/players/occult_herbmaster.pn